1
00:00:01,120 --> 00:00:03,950
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,950 --> 00:00:07,120
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make 
sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:09,230
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:00:10,890 --> 00:00:13,450
Previously on Fairy Tail:

5
00:00:13,450 --> 00:00:15,060
Together?

6
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,620
That's not it, Erza.

7
00:00:17,620 --> 00:00:21,120
Siegrain and Jellal were a single person!

8
00:00:21,120 --> 00:00:27,140
Then, Etherion was unleashed, and the true 
form of the Tower of Heaven was revealed.

9
00:00:27,140 --> 00:00:31,830
I want her to be her usual self when 
she wakes up from this nightmare.

10
00:00:31,830 --> 00:00:33,900
So I will fight!

11
00:02:07,910 --> 00:02:10,770
I wonder if Natsu and Erza are okay?

12
00:02:10,770 --> 00:02:15,310
They're fine. Because they're 
both Fairy Tail wizards.

13
00:02:15,310 --> 00:02:19,610
You've got that right. All we 
can do now is believe in them.

14
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:29,230
I'm all fired up! More than I've ever been!

15
00:02:29,230 --> 00:02:31,050
You little brat!

16
00:02:31,050 --> 00:02:33,420
I'll end this in an instant!

17
00:02:33,870 --> 00:02:37,670
I'll send you to Hell regretting the 
fact that you ever stood up again!

18
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:41,020
One thing I know is that 
I can be real stubborn.

19
00:02:41,020 --> 00:02:43,050
If you're gonna do it, then 
give me your best shot!

20
00:02:46,780 --> 00:02:47,560
Whoa, there!

21
00:02:50,790 --> 00:02:52,600
Bring it!

22
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:12,440
Titania Falls!

23
00:03:16,950 --> 00:03:17,550
Natsu!

24
00:03:22,340 --> 00:03:24,200
What's wrong? That all you got?

25
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:27,420
You scared a breakin' the 
tower, so you're holding back?

26
00:03:27,420 --> 00:03:28,930
That ain't gonna work on me, bub!

27
00:03:28,930 --> 00:03:32,330
You ain't gonna talk so 
big for long, you brat!

28
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:36,220
Dazzling Blaze of the Fire Dragon!

29
00:03:44,780 --> 00:03:46,990
He's... the tower...

30
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,030
The...

31
00:03:58,000 --> 00:04:02,310
The tower I spent 8 years constructing...

32
00:04:02,310 --> 00:04:03,760
How dare you!

33
00:04:06,430 --> 00:04:09,000
Well, what a <i>shame</i>...

34
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:13,480
I told you, remember? My 
specialty is destroying stuff.

35
00:04:14,250 --> 00:04:18,980
Natsu... He can barely even stand...

36
00:04:18,980 --> 00:04:20,770
You won't get away with it!

37
00:04:30,150 --> 00:04:33,500
What's with this magical 
power? It's making me sick...

38
00:04:33,500 --> 00:04:36,210
The shadows are extending 
backwards to the light source!

39
00:04:36,210 --> 00:04:38,840
Oh, no! This magic is...

40
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:43,650
Fall into the infinite 
darkness, dragon wizard!

41
00:04:44,490 --> 00:04:45,890
Jellal!

42
00:04:48,550 --> 00:04:51,350
Will you let me be killed as well?

43
00:04:58,060 --> 00:05:01,300
You need a body to resurrect Zeref, correct?

44
00:05:02,030 --> 00:05:03,010
Yes.

45
00:05:03,340 --> 00:05:06,870
It's a general requirement 
that the body be of a wizard

46
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:09,790
about as powerful as one 
of the Ten Wizard Saints.

47
00:05:10,490 --> 00:05:15,150
But at this point, it doesn't 
have to be you anymore.

48
00:05:15,150 --> 00:05:17,250
Die together, both of you!

49
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,750
Erza, move!

50
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:27,160
You have nothing to fear.

51
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,890
I will protect you.

52
00:05:28,890 --> 00:05:30,350
Stop it!

53
00:05:30,350 --> 00:05:32,180
Heavenly Body Magic:

54
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:33,810
Altairis!

55
00:05:37,810 --> 00:05:39,930
Erza!

56
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,690
Whoa...

57
00:05:49,690 --> 00:05:51,240
It exploded!

58
00:05:51,630 --> 00:05:54,110
They're okay... Right?

59
00:05:54,940 --> 00:05:56,910
Sho, what's happening?

60
00:05:58,290 --> 00:06:00,770
What is this unsettled feeling I have...

61
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:12,720
You're...

62
00:06:21,450 --> 00:06:22,800
Simon...

63
00:06:26,330 --> 00:06:27,540
Erza...

64
00:06:29,050 --> 00:06:30,050
Simon!

65
00:06:30,650 --> 00:06:33,320
Still crawling around here?

66
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:35,240
You worm...

67
00:06:35,570 --> 00:06:37,490
But, why?

68
00:06:37,490 --> 00:06:38,960
Didn't you escape?

69
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:40,330
Simon!

70
00:06:44,570 --> 00:06:45,650
I'm glad...

71
00:06:47,290 --> 00:06:48,600
...that I...

72
00:06:50,390 --> 00:06:51,970
...could be...

73
00:06:51,970 --> 00:06:53,250
...of help...

74
00:06:54,090 --> 00:06:55,440
..to you...

75
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:56,660
...at last...

76
00:06:57,180 --> 00:07:01,230
I understand! Now, no more talking!

77
00:07:02,390 --> 00:07:04,020
You were...

78
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,690
...always...

79
00:07:05,690 --> 00:07:07,060
...so kind...

80
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,430
...so kind...

81
00:07:13,290 --> 00:07:14,540
Simon...

82
00:07:26,170 --> 00:07:27,440
Simon!

83
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,540
Simon!

84
00:07:31,430 --> 00:07:32,740
I love...

85
00:07:33,150 --> 00:07:34,420
...ed you...

86
00:08:14,610 --> 00:08:17,300
How pointless! How incredibly pointless!

87
00:08:17,300 --> 00:08:20,770
They call that throwing 
away your life, Simon!

88
00:08:20,770 --> 00:08:22,870
This doesn't change a thing!

89
00:08:22,870 --> 00:08:26,900
Because there's no way anyone 
is leaving this tower alive!

90
00:08:26,900 --> 00:08:28,690
Shut up!

91
00:08:39,300 --> 00:08:40,370
He's...

92
00:08:42,830 --> 00:08:45,560
The crazy bastard is eating Etherion!

93
00:09:09,270 --> 00:09:11,290
That's insane!

94
00:09:11,290 --> 00:09:15,150
Ethernano is fused with other 
elements than fire, you know!

95
00:09:17,930 --> 00:09:21,420
Did you seriously think you could power up

96
00:09:21,420 --> 00:09:23,750
by eating such powerful magic 
energy instead of flames?

97
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:27,290
That kind of peabrained thinking 
will lead you to your own downfall!

98
00:09:46,290 --> 00:09:49,980
He's actually absorbing Etherion?

99
00:09:53,690 --> 00:09:55,670
You're the reason...

100
00:09:58,200 --> 00:10:01,240
...that Erza is crying!

101
00:10:02,700 --> 00:10:05,040
I made a promise!

102
00:10:06,050 --> 00:10:08,370
Natsu, take care of Erza.

103
00:10:09,710 --> 00:10:12,380
I made a promise!

104
00:10:12,380 --> 00:10:13,630
You cocky bastard!

105
00:10:13,950 --> 00:10:14,950
Meteor!

106
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:24,060
You'll never be able to 
catch me at this speed!

107
00:10:36,780 --> 00:10:39,850
Impossible! I can't lose!

108
00:10:42,300 --> 00:10:44,820
I'm making a kingdom of freedom!

109
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:49,750
Zeref whispered to me in my pain and fear...

110
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:54,750
"Do you desire true freedom?" 
Zeref beckoned...

111
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:58,660
That's right. Only I can sense Zeref!

112
00:10:58,660 --> 00:11:01,050
I am the chosen one!

113
00:11:01,050 --> 00:11:05,050
Zeref and I will create a 
truly free kingdom together!

114
00:11:05,050 --> 00:11:09,310
And you'll make it by taking 
away other people's freedom?

115
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:15,060
Only ones with the will to change 
the world can make history!

116
00:11:15,060 --> 00:11:18,820
Why can't you understand this?

117
00:11:22,850 --> 00:11:24,280
Abyss Break?

118
00:11:24,700 --> 00:11:28,370
You fiend! You plan to 
destroy the tower as well?

119
00:11:28,370 --> 00:11:30,170
8 more years.

120
00:11:30,170 --> 00:11:34,040
No... This time I'll finish it in 5.

121
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:36,380
Zeref, wait for me!

122
00:11:42,630 --> 00:11:45,510
You will never find freedom!

123
00:11:46,520 --> 00:11:51,270
There is no such thing as freedom 
for somebody taken over by ghosts!

124
00:11:53,370 --> 00:11:57,520
Free yourself first, Jellal!

125
00:12:15,490 --> 00:12:16,890
What in the world...

126
00:12:16,890 --> 00:12:18,750
What's happening?

127
00:12:18,750 --> 00:12:21,260
That's got to be Natsu.

128
00:12:21,590 --> 00:12:23,970
Yeah, I agree.

129
00:12:23,970 --> 00:12:27,250
But, is that gonna be okay?

130
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:30,210
It'll be okay... Or so I'd like to think.

131
00:12:30,210 --> 00:12:32,770
But he sure is going wild there...

132
00:12:49,410 --> 00:12:53,200
This is... Natsu's true power.

133
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:55,690
This is...

134
00:12:57,190 --> 00:12:58,760
...a Dragon Slayer!

135
00:13:24,260 --> 00:13:26,750
He even defeated Jellal...

136
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:34,820
The battle I've been fighting 
these 8 years is now over.

137
00:13:35,890 --> 00:13:39,570
Now, everyone is truly free...

138
00:13:41,780 --> 00:13:42,800
Natsu!

139
00:13:55,890 --> 00:13:57,840
You're really incredible...

140
00:13:58,680 --> 00:13:59,680
Really...

141
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:06,860
How pretty!

142
00:14:06,860 --> 00:14:08,450
No, that's...

143
00:14:08,450 --> 00:14:11,840
I can feel a terrible magical 
power coming from that light!

144
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,880
Wait... Then that means...

145
00:14:13,880 --> 00:14:16,560
Could Etherion be going out of control?

146
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:18,490
Out of control? Why?

147
00:14:19,170 --> 00:14:21,310
The magical power of Etherion...

148
00:14:22,210 --> 00:14:28,470
Keeping that great amount of magical power 
in one place can never be stable for long.

149
00:14:28,470 --> 00:14:31,840
A turbulent vortex of magical power with 
no where else to go will burst out,

150
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:33,390
causing a giant explosion...

151
00:14:33,710 --> 00:14:37,240
Whoa! We'll be caught in it as well!

152
00:14:37,240 --> 00:14:38,890
What about Sister and 
the others still inside?

153
00:14:39,860 --> 00:14:43,480
This isn't about who's saving who anymore!

154
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:46,630
We're all going to be wiped out together!

155
00:14:58,090 --> 00:14:59,390
Simon...

156
00:15:29,410 --> 00:15:34,050
Magical power strong enough to deform 
the container... The lacrima...

157
00:15:34,410 --> 00:15:37,520
That's even more destructive 
power than I had imagined.

158
00:15:38,640 --> 00:15:42,480
Even if we get outside, we'll 
be caught up in the explosion.

159
00:15:43,560 --> 00:15:44,400
Damn it!

160
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,350
Is this the end?

161
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:57,220
No... There's no way I'll give up.

162
00:15:58,020 --> 00:16:01,370
Now it's my turn to save you, Natsu.

163
00:16:03,330 --> 00:16:06,270
But it's impossible to hold it back.

164
00:16:06,270 --> 00:16:07,370
What can I do?

165
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:12,850
The tremendous amount of magical 
power this lacrima now stores,

166
00:16:12,850 --> 00:16:15,110
will be fused into your body.

167
00:16:15,110 --> 00:16:21,250
Your body will be deconstructed, and 
then reconstituted into Zeref's.

168
00:16:21,250 --> 00:16:22,510
Fused?

169
00:16:23,860 --> 00:16:30,690
If I can fuse with Etherion, then can I 
control this power? Can I stop the explosion?

170
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,890
I've got to take the chance.

171
00:16:44,180 --> 00:16:48,730
Good. The lacrima is still accepting me.

172
00:16:59,010 --> 00:16:59,910
Erza...

173
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:02,370
Natsu?

174
00:17:03,460 --> 00:17:04,800
What are you doing?

175
00:17:04,800 --> 00:17:09,250
Erza... You're putting 
yourself into the lacrima?

176
00:17:09,940 --> 00:17:13,590
This is the only way to stop Etherion.

177
00:17:14,140 --> 00:17:16,250
Stop Etherion?

178
00:17:17,550 --> 00:17:20,040
Yes. Look around you.

179
00:17:20,530 --> 00:17:25,960
This tower will shortly explode 
as Etherion goes out of control.

180
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:30,400
But if I can fuse with 
Etherion and suppress it...

181
00:17:30,770 --> 00:17:32,880
What are you saying, you idiot!

182
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:34,480
If you do that, you'll...

183
00:17:35,910 --> 00:17:36,920
Erza!

184
00:17:38,740 --> 00:17:41,090
Don't worry about it any more!

185
00:17:41,580 --> 00:17:43,080
I'll stop it for sure!

186
00:17:43,380 --> 00:17:44,410
Don't!

187
00:17:46,520 --> 00:17:47,940
Stop it!

188
00:17:47,940 --> 00:17:49,030
Erza!

189
00:17:53,890 --> 00:17:54,930
Natsu...

190
00:18:03,010 --> 00:18:06,560
I couldn't have lived without Fairy Tail.

191
00:18:07,460 --> 00:18:11,850
A world without my friends is unthinkable.

192
00:18:12,970 --> 00:18:18,200
You are all just that important to me.

193
00:18:20,300 --> 00:18:21,440
Erza...

194
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:31,760
If I can save everyone...

195
00:18:31,760 --> 00:18:33,990
...then I do so without hesitation.

196
00:18:34,620 --> 00:18:35,960
Even if it takes this body...

197
00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:39,300
...so be it!

198
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:46,630
Erza!

199
00:18:46,630 --> 00:18:48,190
Get out of there, Erza!

200
00:18:48,910 --> 00:18:52,100
Natsu, take care of everyone for me.

201
00:18:54,110 --> 00:18:58,250
Because I'll always be by your side...

202
00:19:06,410 --> 00:19:09,660
Erza!

203
00:19:12,610 --> 00:19:14,290
It's exploding!

204
00:19:16,060 --> 00:19:17,750
No, it's not!

205
00:19:18,560 --> 00:19:22,180
Etherion is heading up into the sky!

206
00:19:36,900 --> 00:19:38,460
It disappeared!

207
00:19:38,460 --> 00:19:40,280
Etherion went into the sky!

208
00:19:40,280 --> 00:19:43,700
Erza! Natsu!

209
00:19:58,350 --> 00:20:00,340
That's such a horrid wound...

210
00:20:00,340 --> 00:20:03,940
It will be quite difficult 
for you to see again, yes...

211
00:20:04,280 --> 00:20:07,450
Now, now... I'm asking you 
nicely so no complaining.

212
00:20:07,450 --> 00:20:12,040
She's got such a pretty face, 
have some compassion would you?

213
00:20:13,270 --> 00:20:15,050
Come here a moment.

214
00:20:15,050 --> 00:20:16,980
Owwww!

215
00:20:17,260 --> 00:20:20,600
You're not thinking of laying hands 
on her when she's older, are you?

216
00:20:21,710 --> 00:20:23,820
O-Of course not...

217
00:20:25,730 --> 00:20:27,020
Where is she from?

218
00:20:27,020 --> 00:20:30,950
Rob was helping her out...

219
00:20:30,950 --> 00:20:32,010
Rob?

220
00:20:32,320 --> 00:20:33,880
Where is he now?

221
00:20:35,470 --> 00:20:37,710
It seems he's dead...

222
00:20:59,430 --> 00:21:00,430
How is it?

223
00:21:11,360 --> 00:21:12,580
It's healed!

224
00:21:13,110 --> 00:21:14,320
Can you see?

225
00:21:15,690 --> 00:21:16,750
Yes...

226
00:21:17,090 --> 00:21:19,140
Then get out, immediately.

227
00:21:19,650 --> 00:21:21,960
I hate humans, get it?

228
00:21:24,390 --> 00:21:25,760
It's healed...

229
00:21:30,320 --> 00:21:32,510
You... That eye...

230
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:38,270
You're only crying out of one eye...

231
00:21:40,330 --> 00:21:41,880
That shouldn't be...

232
00:21:42,180 --> 00:21:44,500
I didn't make an error
while mixing the medicine...

233
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:45,560
And yet...

234
00:21:45,980 --> 00:21:47,060
It's okay.

235
00:21:50,100 --> 00:21:54,870
I've already cried out 
half my tears, you see.

236
00:22:04,730 --> 00:22:05,600
Where am I?

237
00:23:55,730 --> 00:24:00,090
Natsu, it seems like our new 
guild is finally finished!

238
00:24:00,090 --> 00:24:02,770
Ooh! I can't wait to check it out!

239
00:24:02,770 --> 00:24:06,720
It's finally been rebuilt, so don't go 
destroying it all of a sudden, okay?

240
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:10,730
Hey, since when have I been the 
type to go around destroying stuff?

241
00:24:10,730 --> 00:24:13,380
Is he that oblivious? Sheesh...

242
00:24:14,010 --> 00:24:15,910
Next time: Home!

243
00:24:16,390 --> 00:24:19,710
Things break because Gray 
and Erza go crazy, right?

244
00:24:19,710 --> 00:24:22,310
But it's usually you who 
starts the fights, Natsu.

245
00:24:22,310 --> 00:24:24,050
So it's all my fault?!

246
00:24:24,050 --> 00:24:26,300


